<summary>ðŸ¤– Prompt for AI Agents</summary>

```
In src/bin/doc-gen.rs around lines 87 to 94, the List branch prints a hard-coded
tool list which duplicates definitions in src/doc_generator.rs and src/lib.rs;
replace the static printout by invoking the existing documentation generator to
produce the up-to-date tool list. Specifically, call the function (e.g.,
DocGenerator::generate_tools_documentation() or the appropriate public helper)
to obtain the tools summary/text, and print that result instead of the
hard-coded strings; ensure you only request the concise tool list/view (not the
full report) or trim the generated output to match the previous List behavior,
and handle any errors from the generator by logging a sensible message and
exiting non-zero if generation fails.
```

</details>

